formatterData.formattedText:
<c:FragmentDefinition
	xmlns="sap.m"
	xmlns:c="sap.ui.core"
>
	<Button
		id="idButtonFragmentController2"
		text="{
			formatter: '.formatter.formatValueFragmentController2',
			test: [1, 2, 3],
			test2: ['abc', 'asd'],
			test3: {
				test: [1, 2, 3],
				test2: ['abc', 'asd']
			},
			test4: [{
				path: 'asd'
			}, {
				path: 123
			}]
		}"
		press="eventHandler11"
	/>
	<Button text="{= ${/SupportModel}}"/>
	<Button text="{Test}"/>
	<Button
		icon="asd"
		text="{
			path: 'test'
		}"
	/>
	<Text
		text="{
			path: 'Test>Confidence',
			type: 'sap.ui.model.type.Integer'
		} %"
		wrapping="false"
	/>
	<Text
		text="{
			path: 'Test>Confidence',
			type: 'sap.ui.model.type.Integer'
		} {
			path: 'Test>Confidence',
			type: 'sap.ui.model.type.Integer'
		}"
		wrapping="false"
	/>
	<HBox
		justifyContent="End"
		visible="{=
			${ZoneModel>ProcessingState} === '1' ||
			${ZoneModel>ProcessingState} === '6' ||
			${ZoneModel>ProcessingState} === '5'
		}"
	/>
	<HBox visible="{=
		${device>/isDesktop} &&
		${
			path: 'SupportModel>asd',
			formatter: '.documentStatusMapping.getPhInvGroupIsPostingAllowed'
		}
	}"/>
	<Button visible="{=
		(
			(
				${viewModel>IS_SINGLE_PRODUCT_OFFER}
			) || (
				(
					${viewModel>LEVEL} === 'STORE_FORMAT_LEVEL' ||
					${viewModel>LEVEL} === 'PRODUCT_LEVEL'
				) &&
				!${viewModel>IS_SINGLE_PRODUCT_OFFER}
			)
		)
	}"/>
	<Button visible="{=
		!(${SupportModel>/Layout})
		.startsWith('Three')
	}"/>
</c:FragmentDefinition>
